| DATE_FORMAT(dt, '%d %M %Y') |
+-----------------------------+
| 10 August 2015              |
| 17 August 2016              |
| 31 December 2017            |
| 04 August 2015              |
+-----------------------------+
4 rows in set (0.00 sec)
mysql> SELECT DATE_FORMAT(ts, '%d %M %Y, %k:%i:%s') FROM belajar_date;
