| DATE_FORMAT(ts, '%d %M %Y, %k:%i:%s') |
+---------------------------------------+
| 10 August 2015, 8:30:15               |
| 17 August 2016, 10:01:01              |
| 31 December 2017, 23:59:59            |
| 04 August 2015, 15:34:14              |
+---------------------------------------+
4 rows in set (0.03 sec)
